# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s16b_f2217e9d:

    # "Less than a minute, and we’re already falling behind. I watch Mariah’s taillights as she speeds up the road, horn blaring to scare away the cars unfortunate enough to be in her lane."
    "Menos de un minuto, y ya nos estamos quedando atrás. Observo las luces traseras de Mariah mientras acelera por la carretera, tocando la bocina para espantar a los autos desafortunados que están en su carril."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s16b_748919ec:

    # "I’m going as fast as I dare to, worried about cops that could be lurking around one of the bends in the road."
    "Voy tan rápido como me atrevo, preocupada por los policías que podrían estar escondidos en alguna de las curvas del camino."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s16b_1a0a6999:

    # "But I can’t let her out of my sights. There’s no room to pass yet, but I have to watch for an opportunity."
    "Pero no puedo perderla de vista. Todavía no hay espacio para adelantar, pero tengo que buscar una oportunidad."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s16b_90ebd151:

    # "With one hand, Marina clutches the headrest bar of her seat. Then she leans over and past my face, nearly causing me to swerve from shock."
    "Con una mano, Marina se aferra a la barra del reposacabezas de su asiento. Luego se inclina y pasa frente a mi cara, casi haciendo que me desvíe del susto."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s16b_e9dd493e:

    # Amber "What are you-"
    Amber "Что ты-"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s16b_6d9935db:

    # "She grabs my seatbelt and buckles me in. Then she does the same for herself."
    "Toma mi cinturón de seguridad y me lo abrocha. Luego hace lo mismo con el suyo."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s16b_9a8143f6:

    # Marina "Okay, now that we’re at least not gonna die if you hit something…"
    Marina "Теперь, по крайней мере, мы не умрем въехав во что-нибудь…"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s16b_3206532a:

    # Marina "Can you tell me what exactly is happening?"
    Marina "Может ты посвятишь меня в то, что происходит?"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s16b_e0c668cc:

    # "She sounds a little frantic, and a little curious."
    "Suena un poco frenética, y un poco curiosa."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s16b_71bbc387:

    # Amber "Okay, so, do you remember Balanced Rock?"
    Amber "Да. Помнишь “Балансирующий камень”?"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s16b_9fe03d9f:

    # "It wasn’t one of the places that we visited earlier today, but it’s one of the spots that’s on posters and in lots of the ads."
    "No era uno de los lugares que visitamos hoy, pero es uno de los sitios que aparecen en pósters y en muchos anuncios."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s16b_c70b2e92:

    # Marina "I think so. Or at least hearing about it."
    Marina "Думаю да. Ну или я точно слышала о нем."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s16b_397919ec:

    # Amber "There used to be another really famous rock right next to it. Smaller, but a similar shape and everything. They called it 'Chip Off the Old Block.'"
    Amber "Рядом находился еще один камень. Он был меньше, но точно такой же по форме. Его называли “Chip Off the Old Block” - “Маленькая копия Балансирующего камня”."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s16b_ac0ee9da:

    # Marina "What do you mean ‘used to be?’"
    Marina "Что ты имеешь в виду под “был?”"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s16b_ab346f74:

    # Amber "I was getting to that. A long time ago, like 50 years or something, it fell. Now you can’t even tell it apart from the rest of the rocks on the ground."
    Amber "Я собиралсь к этому перейти. Когда-то давно, 50 лет назад или около того, он рухнул. В его нынешнем состоянии ты вряд ли отличишь его от обычных лежащих на земле валунов."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s16b_85b4d612:

    # Marina "Fifty years… So that was…"
    Marina "Пятьдесят лет… То есть когда…"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s16b_92a13582:

    # "Her eyes go wide in understanding, a fact which I look away from Mariah’s rear to take in."
    "Sus ojos se abren de par en par al comprender, un hecho que aparto la mirada de la parte trasera de Mariah para apreciar."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s16b_4d91e9c1:

    # Marina "So it was still standing when the miner came through!"
    Marina "Значит он был все еще там, когда старатель проходил через это место!"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s16b_95351173:

    # Amber "Yeah, exactly. I’ll bet you anything he hid the treasure between Balanced Rock and what used to be Chip."
    Amber "Именно. Ставлю все что угодно, что он зарыл клад между “Балансирующим камнем” и тем, что теперь осталось от “копии”."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s16b_6767e805:

    # "I look over again to smile at her, only to see genuine admiration and awe in her face. Her eyes are wide, and her mouth slightly open."
    "Vuelvo a mirarla para sonreírle, solo para ver admiración genuina y asombro en su rostro. Sus ojos están muy abiertos, y su boca ligeramente entreabierta."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s16b_0eb47921:

    # "Like always, I can’t look at her for too long, or it starts to make me uncomfortable. Nothing I’ve said or done is that impressive. Even Mariah knew about Chip."
    "Como siempre, no puedo mirarla por mucho tiempo, o empieza a hacerme sentir incómoda. Nada de lo que he dicho o hecho es tan impresionante. Hasta Mariah sabía lo de Chip."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s16b_2ddc9466:

    # "But instead of singing my praises again, she just faces ahead with a little smile."
    "Pero en lugar de volver a alabarme, solo mira al frente con una pequeña sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s16b_b253d19f:

    # "Then her face crumples up."
    "Luego su rostro se arruga."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s16b_037408c8:

    # Marina "Amber!"
    Marina "Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s16b_85724154:

    # Amber "I see it."
    Amber "Вижу."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s16b_30f62a7c:

    # "A semi has begun pulling out into the road ahead of us. There’s no passing lane, so I can’t get around him that way."
    "Un tráiler ha comenzado a salir a la carretera frente a nosotros. No hay carril para adelantar, así que no puedo rebasarlo por ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s16b_d0cbde77:

    # Amber "Dammit!"
    Amber "Твою мать!"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s16b_639bebb0:

    # "I tap the brakes, since I’ll have to stop and wait for him to get onto the highway."
    "Piso el freno, ya que tendré que detenerme y esperar a que entre a la autopista."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s16b_3303d3cc:

    # "Ahead, I can still see Mariah, but just barely. A few of the cars between us have exited, but her lead has grown."
    "Adelante, todavía puedo ver a Mariah, pero apenas. Algunos de los autos entre nosotros se han salido, pero su ventaja ha aumentado."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s16b_906e470c:

    # "And so I make a quick, reckless decision."
    "Y así tomo una decisión rápida e imprudente."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s16b_53c32839:

    # Amber "Hold onto something."
    Amber "Держись."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s16b_174311c2:

    # Marina "What are you-"
    Marina "Что ты-"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s16b_cb28b6e0:

    # "I don’t wait for her to finish her question, since she grabs onto her seat as she asks it."
    "No espero a que termine su pregunta, ya que se agarra de su asiento mientras la hace."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s16b_b0f18f44:

    # "To answer, I yank the wheel to the left and into the other lane, even though it’s a no-pass zone." with vpunch
    "В качестве ответа я выворачиваю колеса влево, намереваясь выехать на другую полосу, несмотря на то, что ехать по ней нельзя." with vpunch

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s16b_97c9a2b5:

    # "Headlights far ahead are speeding toward us, maybe a quarter mile away."
    "Los faros adelante se acercan a toda velocidad hacia nosotros, a un cuarto de milla de distancia."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s16b_683c4635:

    # "Getting closer."
    "Cada vez más cerca."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s16b_702de921:

    # "A concrete barrier prevents me from going any further to the left. I smash the gas pedal to the floor, putting all my weight on it."
    "Una barrera de concreto me impide ir más a la izquierda. Aplasto el pedal del acelerador hasta el fondo, poniendo todo mi peso sobre él."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s16b_57472e45:

    # "Marina begins to moan with dread at the oncoming car. It’s a wordless sound, or maybe the start of my name."
    "Marina empieza a gemir de pavor ante el auto que se aproxima. Es un sonido sin palabras, o quizás el inicio de mi nombre."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s16b_398c69ea:

    # "My heart is in my throat and I can feel beads of sweat on my forehead. One slides down into my eye but I can’t wipe it away."
    "Tengo el corazón en la garganta y siento gotas de sudor en la frente. Una se desliza hacia mi ojo, pero no puedo limpiarla."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s16b_769a6a91:

    # "We’re even with the semi now, who seems to be stopping. He probably noticed me and is waiting for me to complete my illegal pass."
    "Ahora estamos al nivel del tráiler, que parece estar deteniéndose. Probablemente me notó y está esperando que complete mi adelantamiento ilegal."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s16b_aeadf6bc:

    # "The car ahead of us is close enough that I can see it in our headlight beams; it’s a maroon SUV. They’re braking as they approach."
    "El auto frente a nosotros está lo suficientemente cerca como para verlo con nuestros faros; es una camioneta SUV granate. Están frenando mientras se acercan."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s16b_d0834536:

    # "But I’m still accelerating, going so fast that I couldn’t stop in time even if I wanted to."
    "Pero yo sigo acelerando, yendo tan rápido que no podría detenerme a tiempo aunque quisiera."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s16b_4c5f954d:

    # "Like a missile, we shoot forward. I’m at least double the speed limit right now."
    "Como un misil, nos lanzamos hacia adelante. Voy al menos al doble del límite de velocidad ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s16b_cf0ecd96:

    # "We come even with the front of the semi, which is hardly rolling."
    "Llegamos al nivel del frente del tráiler, que apenas rueda."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s16b_5b658091:

    # "The SUV has come to a complete stop, but there’s barely any room between it and the semi now."
    "La SUV se ha detenido por completo, pero apenas hay espacio entre ella y el tráiler ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s16b_678f9683:

    # "And then suddenly we’re past the cab of the truck."
    "Y de repente, pasamos la cabina del camión."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s16b_03ae1e09:

    # "I wrench the wheel to the right; hard right, throwing us back into our own lane."
    "Giro el volante a la derecha; fuerte a la derecha, lanzándonos de vuelta a nuestro carril."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s16b_a7d645b6:

    # "We zoom past the stopped SUV, who gives me a well-deserved horn blaring. The bassy sound of the semi’s horn also booms behind us."
    "Pasamos zumbando junto a la SUV detenida, que me toca la bocina merecidamente. El sonido grave de la bocina del tráiler también retumba detrás de nosotros."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s16b_e0bd7262:

    # "But it doesn’t matter, because we’re okay. We didn’t die."
    "Pero no importa, porque estamos bien. No morimos."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s16b_26dcf664:

    # "A need to breathe hits me, and I realize that I’ve been holding it in."
    "Me golpea la necesidad de respirar, y me doy cuenta de que he estado conteniendo el aliento."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s16b_4577c96c:

    # "I sigh, adrenaline still coursing through me."
    "Suspiro, con la adrenalina aún recorriéndome."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s16b_466dd1e1:

    # Marina "Oh my god, Amber!"
    Marina "Боже мой, Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s16b_bafdf6ca:

    # "Her voice cracks, and she starts to laugh. Hysterically."
    "Su voz se quiebra, y empieza a reír. Histéricamente."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s16b_4d5a172b:

    # "I do too, laughing away the anxiety of the last half-minute. It felt like much longer."
    "Yo también lo hago, riéndome para disipar la ansiedad del último medio minuto. Se sintió como mucho más tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s16b_299f1a29:

    # "And it’s not entirely over yet."
    "Y aún no ha terminado del todo."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s16b_298ca271:

    # Amber "Don’t get too comfy."
    Amber "Не слишкмо расслабляйся."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s16b_5f7964ff:

    # "Her hands shoot back to where she was hanging on."
    "Sus manos vuelven a dispararse hacia donde se agarraba."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s16b_bb7e85b9:

    # Marina "Uh oh."
    Marina "О-оу."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s16b_0e053691:

    # "Just ahead, Mariah still has a lead but it’s shrinking quickly. I wonder if she saw how I caught up."
    "Justo adelante, Mariah todavía tiene ventaja, pero se está reduciendo rápidamente. Me pregunto si vio cómo la alcancé."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s16b_bf34f29a:

    # "Jamming the gas pedal down again, I start to narrow the distance even more." with vpunch
    "Снова выжимая педаль газа на полную, я стараюсь еще больше сократить дистанцию." with vpunch

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s16b_f848ae8d:

    # "She takes the exit for Arches just a few seconds ahead of me. We blaze through the entry point, flashing our passes at rangers who barely have time to check them."
    "Toma la salida hacia Arches apenas unos segundos antes que yo. Pasamos a toda velocidad por el punto de entrada, mostrando nuestros pases a los guardabosques que apenas tienen tiempo de revisarlos."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s16b_9c27e033:

    # "Even in the darkness, there are lots of people on the sides of the road."
    "Incluso en la oscuridad, hay mucha gente a los lados del camino."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s16b_c669170a:

    # "I wonder if anyone else has had the same realization we did, about Chip."
    "Me pregunto si alguien más habrá tenido la misma revelación que nosotras sobre Chip."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s16b_8f942d14:

    # "Mariah’s starting to gain ground again, so I mash the accelerator farther down. But her motorhome is newer than mine, and it’s hard for me to keep up."
    "Mariah está empezando a ganar terreno de nuevo, así que piso el acelerador a fondo. Pero su casa rodante es más nueva que la mía, y me cuesta mantener el ritmo."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s16b_70819c12:

    # "If I’m going to beat her there, I’ll have to do it soon."
    "Si voy a ganarle llegando allí, tendré que hacerlo pronto."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s16b_6e18cbd8:

    # "I check to make sure that Marina’s still holding on tight."
    "Me aseguro de que Marina todavía se esté sujetando fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s16b_358a35ff:

    # "She is."
    "Lo está."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s16b_62339218:

    # "Just a few feet behind Mariah’s RV, I illegally swing into the other lane yet again."
    "A solo unos metros de la casa rodante de Mariah, me cambio ilegalmente al otro carril una vez más."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:305
translate spanish hwb_s16b_569dd8af:

    # "This is even more risky because of the way the road curves all over the canyon. An oncoming car could round a bend and completely blindside us."
    "Esto es aún más arriesgado por la forma en que el camino serpentea por todo el cañón. Un auto que venga en sentido contrario podría doblar una curva y tomarnos completamente por sorpresa."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:307
translate spanish hwb_s16b_aa96ec37:

    # "Hope that doesn’t happen."
    "Espero que eso no pase."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s16b_6b0f3014:

    # "By pushing the RV to its absolute limits, I’m able to break even with Mariah. Looking over, I can see a wild flair in her eyes, hair disheveled. Her expression changes to one of shock when she notices us beside her."
    "Al llevar la casa rodante al límite absoluto, logro igualar a Mariah. Al mirar hacia ella, puedo ver un destello salvaje en sus ojos, el cabello despeinado. Su expresión cambia a una de shock cuando nos nota a nuestro lado."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:311
translate spanish hwb_s16b_b299bc3c:

    # "I relish in the look of disbelief as I nudge the wheel to the right."
    "Disfruto su mirada de incredulidad mientras giro el volante hacia la derecha."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:313
translate spanish hwb_s16b_e4899819:

    # "There’s a godawful scraping as the motorhome brushes against Mariah’s. Her eyes, as well as Marina’s, widen."
    "Hay un chirrido horrible cuando la casa rodante roza la de Mariah. Sus ojos, así como los de Marina, se abren de par en par."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s16b_8e01dbc6:

    # "Seconds after we pull apart, Mariah’s vehicle lurches towards us, and again there’s a sound that makes me want to rip my ears off. I fight to keep control of the motorhome and stay on the road."
    "Segundos después de separarnos, el vehículo de Mariah se lanza hacia nosotras, y de nuevo hay un sonido que me hace querer arrancarme las orejas. Lucho por mantener el control de la casa rodante y permanecer en el camino."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s16b_d5d10d9d:

    # "Awestruck bystanders watch as we pass by, but I hardly register them."
    "Los transeúntes atónitos nos observan pasar, pero apenas los registro."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:319
translate spanish hwb_s16b_5e6e8318:

    # "Still neck and neck, we continue toward Balanced Rock."
    "Todavía lado a lado, continuamos hacia la Roca Equilibrada."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s16b_7967691b:

    # "Through insane luck or divine intervention or something, the road ahead is clear."
    "Por una suerte increíble, intervención divina o algo así, el camino adelante está despejado."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s16b_38877b02:

    # "I won't try to shove them off the road again, because there are now steep dropoffs that could actually be fatal."
    "No volveré a intentar sacarlos del camino, porque ahora hay precipicios pronunciados que podrían ser fatales."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s16b_59073c77:

    # "But I do have to do something to gain an edge. Just arriving seconds before her isn't enough."
    "Pero sí tengo que hacer algo para obtener una ventaja. Llegar solo segundos antes que ella no es suficiente."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s16b_eb3a3d7e:

    # "A sign, visible for just a split second, informs us that there are five miles to Balanced Rock."
    "Un letrero, visible solo por una fracción de segundo, nos informa que faltan cinco millas para la Roca Equilibrada."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s16b_7f509d22:

    # "What might have been an arrow for an exit has been scuffed to illegibility."
    "Lo que pudo haber sido una flecha para una salida está tan desgastado que es ilegible."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s16b_bea66097:

    # "Maybe that's our chance."
    "Quizás esa sea nuestra oportunidad."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:333
translate spanish hwb_s16b_28770de0:

    # "Up ahead, barely illuminated by a flickering lamp, the road splits into two directions. A sign in the middle is smashed and folded in on itself, probably the result of someone's reckless driving."
    "Más adelante, apenas iluminado por una farola parpadeante, el camino se divide en dos direcciones. Un letrero en el medio está destrozado y doblado sobre sí mismo, probablemente resultado de la conducción imprudente de alguien."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:335
translate spanish hwb_s16b_611bbd0f:

    # "One of these paths leads to Balanced Rock, but I don't know which. I'm willing to bet Mariah doesn't either, though."
    "Uno de estos caminos lleva a la Roca Equilibrada, pero no sé cuál. Apuesto a que Mariah tampoco lo sabe."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s16b_737a1f5b:

    # "From Marina's window, I can see Mariah shoot me one final death glare, before they rocket off down the exit."
    "Desde la ventana de Marina, puedo ver a Mariah lanzarme una última mirada asesina, antes de que salgan disparadas por la salida."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:378
translate spanish hwb_s16b_3a410654:

    # "We stay on the other branch, though I'm back in the proper lane now."
    "Nosotras nos quedamos en la otra rama, aunque ahora estoy de vuelta en el carril correcto."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:380
translate spanish hwb_s16b_ee96c1ae:

    # "Just gotta hope it's the right branch."
    "Solo hay que esperar que sea la rama correcta."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:382
translate spanish hwb_s16b_81a62bd0:

    # "As I start to calm down yet again, I realize my legs are shaking."
    "Mientras empiezo a calmarme una vez más, me doy cuenta de que me tiemblan las piernas."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:386
translate spanish hwb_s16b_03443826:

    # "Marina cranes around to watch Mariah’s vehicle, which is quickly disappearing into the murk. Once it’s fully out of sight, she turns back to me, her face as white as her knuckles."
    "Marina se gira para ver el vehículo de Mariah, que desaparece rápidamente en la penumbra. Una vez que está fuera de la vista, se vuelve hacia mí, con la cara tan blanca como sus nudillos."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:390
translate spanish hwb_s16b_4ff6641b:

    # Amber "You uh… You okay?"
    Amber "Ты… Ты как?"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s16b_b0f159d1:

    # "Guilt stabs me - I may have seriously traumatized her. With two incidents. Within minutes of each other."
    "La culpa me apuñala: puede que la haya traumatizado seriamente. Con dos incidentes. A minutos el uno del otro."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s16b_e0f71eb4:

    # "After taking a deep breath, she unclenches her fists."
    "Después de respirar hondo, afloja los puños."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s16b_a1dd357e:

    # Marina "Can we never, ever do that again?"
    Marina "Давай больше никогда не будем так делать?"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:402
translate spanish hwb_s16b_1ebe1473:

    # Marina "That was insane. Super insane. Like, oh my god. I thought I was going to die."
    Marina "Это было дико. Безумно. Просто кошмар. Я думала, что умру."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s16b_8e8bdd18:

    # Marina "Wait."
    Marina "Подожди."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s16b_d3059282:

    # Marina "Did we... Did we die?"
    Marina "Мы... Мы умерли, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:412
translate spanish hwb_s16b_b06c728c:

    # Marina "Am I just imagining this now?"
    Marina "Am I just imagining this now?"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s16b_9f70d1af:

    # Amber "I don’t think you could imagine stuff if you were dead, kid."
    Amber "Я не думаю, что ты бы могла видеть все это, если бы ты умерла, солнце."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s16b_e6db6c5d:

    # Marina "That’s the kind of thing a dead person would say!"
    Marina "Это именно то, что сказал бы мертвый человек!"

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s16b_1ea1cd67:

    # Marina "Like in that one movie, where it was all about the guy who could talk to dead people, except-"
    Marina "Прямо как в том фильме про парня, который мог общаться с мертвецами..."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s16b_d024d0fb:

    # Amber "Fine, I’m ninety percent sure we’re not dead, then."
    Amber "Окей, но я на девяносто процентов уверена, что мы не мертвы."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s16b_69d7b147:

    # Marina "Okay."
    Marina "Ладно."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s16b_a199a70a:

    # Marina "Okay. Ninety percent."
    Marina "Ладно. Девяносто процентов."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s16b_17590869:

    # Marina "That’s not bad."
    Marina "Не такой и плохой шанс."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:441
translate spanish hwb_s16b_5f319632:

    # Marina "Besides, it could be worse. If that ghost movie thing happened, that same director could have ended up destroying a beloved animated series down the road."
    Marina "Кроме того, могло бы быть и хуже. Как с тем фильмом про призраков, после которого режиссер своими руками уничтожил всю столь любимую серию фильмов."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:445
translate spanish hwb_s16b_6b643ace:

    # Marina "Glad nothing like that ever happened."
    Marina "Хорошо, что этого не случилось."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:449
translate spanish hwb_s16b_5ee9bacf:

    # Marina "And being a ghost might be kinda cool too. You could spy on people without them ever knowing."
    Marina "Но быть призраком может быть довольно круто. Ты можешь следить за людьми, а они не будут даже этого знать."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:453
translate spanish hwb_s16b_d56c8219:

    # Amber "I’ll keep that in mind if there’s ever someone I wanna haunt."
    Amber "Буду иметь в виду, на случай если появится кто-то, кого я захочу преследовать."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:455
translate spanish hwb_s16b_26f81092:

    # "Our voices are shaky, even though our conversation isn’t serious. I keep checking the rearview, expecting to see the headlights of Mariah’s approaching vengeance, but so far we’re in the clear."
    "Nuestras voces tiemblan, aunque nuestra conversación no es seria. Sigo revisando el espejo retrovisor, esperando ver los faros de la venganza de Mariah acercándose, pero hasta ahora estamos a salvo."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:459
translate spanish hwb_s16b_60d6dc13:

    # "Each passing minute that we don't see the Rock itself, though, makes me worry that we took the wrong turn."
    "Sin embargo, cada minuto que pasa sin ver la Roca en sí me preocupa que hayamos tomado el camino equivocado."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:461
translate spanish hwb_s16b_92cb49f7:

    # "Right on the verge of turning around and tailing Mariah, another sign suddenly looms up ahead of us."
    "Justo al borde de dar la vuelta y seguir a Mariah, otro letrero aparece de repente frente a nosotros."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:463
translate spanish hwb_s16b_209b970a:

    # "We’ve reached Balanced Rock."
    "Hemos llegado a Balanced Rock."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:465
translate spanish hwb_s16b_712c6fa0:

    # "I slow down as we approach the parking area."
    "Reduzco la velocidad al acercarnos al área de estacionamiento."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:467
translate spanish hwb_s16b_551ac6b3:

    # "While not empty, there are far fewer people here than there were at Double Arch earlier today."
    "Aunque no está vacío, hay mucha menos gente aquí que en Double Arch hoy más temprano."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:469
translate spanish hwb_s16b_9876014a:

    # "A good number of them look like they might just be sightseers, since they’re standing around talking or looking at the stars instead of searching."
    "Un buen número de ellos parecen ser solo turistas, ya que están parados hablando o mirando las estrellas en lugar de buscar."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:471
translate spanish hwb_s16b_7c59a719:

    # "Parking is easy, since there are a lots of open spaces."
    "Estacionar es fácil, ya que hay muchos espacios libres."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s16b_a08fdd91:

    # "When I stand up, my legs wobble. I stumble, grabbing Marina’s shoulder for support. She smiles at me, but doesn’t say anything."
    "Cuando me levanto, las piernas me tiemblan. Tropiezo y agarro el hombro de Marina para apoyarme. Ella me sonríe, pero no dice nada."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s16b_a30a32f2:

    # "No more jokes to crack."
    "No más bromas que hacer."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s16b_3f01cad0:

    # "It’s time to get serious."
    "Es hora de ponerse serias."

# game/script/hwb_s16b.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s16b_0d25dee8:

    # "We grab our equipment and hurry out into the night air."
    "Agarramos nuestro equipo y salimos corriendo al aire nocturno."

